OWL and SWRL
What is SWRL Tab? 
The SWRL Tab is an extension to the Protégé-OWL Pluginthat 
permits the creation and execution of SWRL rules. 
The editor can be used to create SWRL rules, edit existing SWRL 
rules, and read and write SWRL rules.
